divs: Sighting DetailsI saw a UFO. Actually my camera saw it because at the moment of shot i didn`t see it with my own eyes.I took this shot with my nokia n95 phone which has decent camera on it. it couldn`t be a bird because birds appear to small and somethimes not at all when i shot them with my phone. Shape of the ufo in my opinion couldn`t be a plane eather because there are no planes of that shape. When I enlarged the photo and adjusted contrast on the image i noticed that it is symmetrical in shape but distorted on one side, I think this is because it was moving it one direction. But i think it`s speed was not so fast because shutter on n95 phones is not so fast. I have found on the internet that people shot ufo-s on cameras that have sensors sensitive to infrared light, i tested my phone camera and it is sensitive to infrared also.
